00198 void ErrorAndStatus::parseYouBotErrorFlags() const {
00199   // Bouml preserved body begin 0007EAF1
00200    // std::stringstream errorMessageStream;
00201    // errorMessageStream << "Joint " << this->jointNumber << " ";
00202     std::string errorMessage;
00203    // errorMessage = errorMessageStream.str();
00204 
00205 
00206     if (value & OVER_CURRENT) {
00207       LOG(warning) << errorMessage << "over current";
00208       //    throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "got over current");
00209     }
00210 
00211     if (value & UNDER_VOLTAGE) {
00212       LOG(warning) << errorMessage << "under voltage";
00213       //    throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "got under voltage");
00214     }
00215 
00216     if (value & OVER_VOLTAGE) {
00217       LOG(warning) << errorMessage << "over voltage";
00218       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "got over voltage");
00219     }
00220 
00221     if (value & OVER_TEMPERATURE) {
00222       LOG(warning) << errorMessage << "over temperature";
00223       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "got over temperature");
00224     }
00225 
00226     if (value & MOTOR_HALTED) {
00227       LOG(info) << errorMessage << "is halted";
00228       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "is halted");
00229     }
00230 
00231     if (value & HALL_SENSOR_ERROR) {
00232       LOG(warning) << errorMessage << "hall sensor problem";
00233       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "got hall sensor problem");
00234     }
00235 
00236     if (value & PWM_MODE_ACTIVE) {
00237       LOG(info) << errorMessage << "PWM mode active";
00238       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "the cycle time is violated");
00239     }
00240 
00241     if (value & VELOCITY_MODE) {
00242       LOG(info) << errorMessage << "velocity mode active";
00243       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "need to initialize the sinus commutation");
00244     }
00245 
00246     if (value & POSITION_MODE) {
00247       LOG(info) << errorMessage << "position mode active";
00248       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "need to initialize the sinus commutation");
00249     }
00250 
00251     if (value & TORQUE_MODE) {
00252       LOG(info) << errorMessage << "torque mode active";
00253       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "need to initialize the sinus commutation");
00254     }
00255 
00256     if (value & POSITION_REACHED) {
00257       LOG(info) << errorMessage << "position reached";
00258       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "need to initialize the sinus commutation");
00259     }
00260 
00261     if (value & INITIALIZED) {
00262       LOG(info) << errorMessage << "is initialized";
00263       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "need to initialize the sinus commutation");
00264     }
00265 
00266     if (value & TIMEOUT) {
00267       LOG(warning) << errorMessage << "timeout";
00268       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "need to initialize the sinus commutation");
00269     }
00270 
00271     if (value & I2T_EXCEEDED) {
00272       LOG(warning) << errorMessage << "I2t exceeded";
00273       //   throw JointErrorException(errorMessage + "need to initialize the sinus commutation");
00274     }
00275 
00276   // Bouml preserved body end 0007EAF1
00277 }
